sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant EvalAPI as Llama Stack Server<br/>Eval API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant DatasetIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Ragas as Ragas evaluate()<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Ollama as Ollama<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPStep1 as KFP Step 1<br/>retrieve_data
    participant KFPStep2 as KFP Step 2<br/>run_ragas_evaluation
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,Ollama: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation (synchronous, in-process)
        Client->>EvalAPI: POST /v1alpha/eval/benchmarks/{id}/jobs<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        EvalAPI->>DatasetIO: Get evaluation dataset<br/>(in-process call)
        DatasetIO-->>EvalAPI: Dataset rows
        EvalAPI->>Ragas: ragas.evaluate()<br/>(asyncio.to_thread)
        Ragas->>Inference: LLM completion<br/>(LlamaStackInlineLLM via LangChain)
        Inference->>Ollama: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Ollama-->>Inference: LLM response
        Inference-->>Ragas: Completion result
        Ragas->>Inference: Embedding request<br/>(LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings)
        Inference->>Ollama: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>HTTP 11434/TCP
        Ollama-->>Inference: Embedding vectors
        Inference-->>Ragas: Embeddings result
        Ragas-->>EvalAPI: EvaluateResponse<br/>(metrics: answer_relevancy,<br/>context_precision, faithfulness,<br/>context_recall)
        EvalAPI-->>Client: EvaluateResponse<br/>HTTP 200
    end

    rect rgb(230, 235, 250)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (asynchronous, Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>EvalAPI: POST /v1alpha/eval/benchmarks/{id}/jobs<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        EvalAPI->>K8sAPI: Read ConfigMap<br/>trustyai-service-operator-config<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP (SA token)
        K8sAPI-->>EvalAPI: Base image reference
        EvalAPI->>KFP: Healthz pre-flight check<br/>GET /apis/v1beta1/healthz<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
        KFP-->>EvalAPI: OK
        EvalAPI->>KFP: Submit pipeline<br/>create_run_from_pipeline_func<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP (Bearer Token)
        KFP-->>EvalAPI: Run ID
        EvalAPI-->>Client: Job ID (async)<br/>HTTP 202

        Note over KFP,S3: KFP Pipeline Execution
        KFP->>KFPStep1: Execute retrieve_data
        KFPStep1->>EvalAPI: GET datasets<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (llama_stack_client)
        EvalAPI-->>KFPStep1: Dataset rows
        KFPStep1->>KFPStep2: Pass dataset artifact
        KFPStep2->>EvalAPI: LLM + embeddings requests<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (LlamaStackRemoteLLM)
        EvalAPI-->>KFPStep2: Inference results
        KFPStep2->>S3: Write results (JSONL)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP (AWS IAM)
        S3-->>KFPStep2: Write confirmed

        Note over Client,S3: Result Retrieval (polling)
        Client->>EvalAPI: GET /v1alpha/eval/benchmarks/{id}/jobs/{job_id}<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        EvalAPI->>KFP: Poll run state<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP (Bearer Token)
        KFP-->>EvalAPI: Run status (SUCCEEDED)
        EvalAPI->>S3: Fetch results<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP (AWS IAM)
        S3-->>EvalAPI: JSONL result data
        EvalAPI-->>Client: EvaluateResponse<br/>HTTP 200
    end
